# 名词解释：
# Terminologies:
# 宽油：大量的油，很多的油
# Kuanyou: A large amount of oil
# 滑锅：冷油下锅，滑过锅底，使锅的温度迅速提高，并产生油膜，防止粘锅
# Huaguo: Pour cold oil into the wok which can significantly increase the wok temperature and produce the oil isolation to prevent food from sticking to the wok
# 明油：成菜之后淋入一点点葱油，来提高菜品的色泽与明亮度，葱油制作链接
# Mingyou: Drizzle with a touch of spring onion infused oil when the dish is done to brighten up the dish. To know how to make the spring onion infused oil, please click the link below:
# https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K1iUmWhezjA
# 刀口辣椒：干辣椒干花椒炒香炒脆后，手工切碎即为刀口辣椒，香辣麻三位一体，辣度温和，制作链接
# Daokoulajiao: Sauté the dried chilies and Sichuan peppercorns until fragrant and crispy, then crush them by knife. Daokoulajiao is the holy trinity of fragrance, spiciness and numbness, and it’s mild in spiciness. Click on the link below to see how it is made:
# https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=USoC8AqirVA

