0:00:00.000,0:00:01.980
# 首先我们准备鲤鱼1条（约900克）
Firstly, let’s prepare the carp (about 900g)

0:00:01.980,0:00:05.120
# 将鱼敲晕之后去除鱼鳞和内脏清洗干净备用
Stun the fish, and remove its scales and guts, then rinse it for later use

0:00:05.120,0:00:08.160
# 同学们处理鱼的时候最好能将里面的牙齿去除
It’s better to remove its teeth inside as well when preparing

0:00:08.160,0:00:09.960
# 这样能减少腥味
Which can reduce the fishy smell

0:00:19.860,0:00:21.540
# 下一步开始改刀
Next, score the fish

0:00:21.540,0:00:23.780
# 首先在鱼身斜刀切三刀
Make three slant cuts on one side of the carp

0:00:23.780,0:00:25.640
# 然后反过来对切三刀
Turn it around, and make three more cuts

0:00:27.260,0:00:29.080
# 然后再反过来对切三刀
Then flip over the fish and repeat the process

0:00:29.080,0:00:31.100
# 同学们切记不能把鱼边切开
Remember not to cut the edge of the fish

0:00:31.100,0:00:33.460
# 否则在煎的时候鱼身容易烂
Otherwise the carp could easily break down when we pan fry it later

0:00:34.460,0:00:36.440
# 下一步开始准备辅料
Next, let’s prepare the other ingredients

0:00:36.440,0:00:38.600
# 准备五花肉一小块切成小粒备用
Get a small piece of pork belly and dice it into small cubes

0:00:38.660,0:00:41.020
# 加五花肉的目的是增加成菜的香味
The purpose of adding pork belly is to lift the fragrance of the dish

0:00:41.020,0:00:42.860
# 也可以直接用猪肉代替
You can also just use some lard instead

0:00:45.720,0:00:47.760
# 准备香菇3个切成小粒备用
Dice three shiitake mushrooms

0:00:47.760,0:00:50.240
# 香菇可以代替味精提升鱼的鲜味
They can replace MSG to increase the umami taste of the fish

0:00:56.180,0:00:58.540
# 准备生姜1小块切成姜粒备用
Then dice a small piece of ginger

0:01:00.660,0:01:03.580
# 准备大蒜几颗切成小粒备用
A few cloves of garlic

0:01:05.275,0:01:07.835
# 最后准备几根小葱白切成小粒备用
And lastly some white parts of scallions

0:01:08.440,0:01:09.920
# 下一步开始制作
Now, let’s cook

0:01:10.140,0:01:11.740
# 首先我们把锅烧热
Firstly, heat up the wok

0:01:11.740,0:01:14.320
# 锅烧热之后加入适量的底油烧至5成热
Once the wok is hot, add in some base oil and heat it up to 50% hot (150 degrees centigrade)

0:01:17.100,0:01:18.840
# 油热之后加入食用盐1勺（约2克）
Add one teaspoon of salt (2g) into the hot oil

0:01:24.240,0:01:26.620
# 然后将鲤鱼下锅开中小火煎5分钟
Then put it the carp and pan fry it for 5 minutes with medium-low heat

0:01:26.620,0:01:29.340
# 这一步的目的是将鲤鱼两面煎香煎黄
This allows both sides of the fish to be golden and fragrant

0:01:33.260,0:01:35.660
# 然后中途将其翻面过来继续煎香
Halfway through, flip the carp over, and continue frying

0:01:35.660,0:01:38.120
# 同学们加盐在油中煎鱼可以防止粘锅
The salt added into the oil can prevent the fish from sticking to the wok

0:01:42.360,0:01:44.380
# 5分钟之后将鲤鱼倒出备用
After 5 minutes, remove the carp from the wok and leave it to rest

0:01:46.780,0:01:49.340
# 锅中再次加入少许底油烧热
Next, add in small amount of base oil and heat it up again

0:01:50.700,0:01:53.800
# 油热之后加入切好的五花肉爆香爆出猪油
Then fry the diced pork belly, and bring out the aroma and fat

0:02:03.540,0:02:06.220
# 猪肉爆香之后加入切好的姜蒜粒爆香
After that, add in the diced ginger and garlic and stir fry until aromatic

0:02:06.220,0:02:08.860
# 同学们猪肉粒必须炒至金黄出油才算香
The pork belly cubes must be fried until golden and its fat released

0:02:19.480,0:02:22.040
# 姜蒜粒炒香之后加入切好的香菇和葱粒
Once ginger and garlic are fragrant, add in the diced shiitake mushrooms and scallions

0:02:33.100,0:02:34.980
# 翻炒均匀之后开始调汁
Stir fry them evenly, and then season the sauce

0:02:35.440,0:02:36.980
# 锅中加入蚝油10克
Add in 10g of oyster sauce

0:02:38.520,0:02:40.720
# 加入生抽酱油6克从锅边淋入
Drizzle in 6g of light soy sauce from the edge of the wok

0:02:45.600,0:02:47.140
# 然后加入啤酒1瓶（500毫升）
Then pour in a bottle of beer (500ml)

0:02:54.260,0:02:56.540
# 大火烧开之后加入食用盐1勺（约1.5克）
After the sauce is boiled with high heat, add in a teaspoon of salt (1.5g)

0:02:58.680,0:03:00.220
# 加入胡椒粉少许
A small amount of ground pepper

0:03:01.080,0:03:02.960
# 加入少许的白糖提鲜
Some sugar to lift the umami

0:03:03.640,0:03:04.860
# 加入半勺五香粉
Half a teaspoon of five spices

0:03:06.880,0:03:08.620
# 加入糖色4克调色
And 4g of caramel

0:03:08.660,0:03:10.900
# 没有糖色的同学可以用老抽代替
Alternatively, you can use dark soy sauce if you don’t have caramel

0:03:12.560,0:03:14.500
# 然后将鲤鱼下锅烧6分钟
Next, add back the carp to braise for 6 minutes

0:03:18.080,0:03:21.040
# 中途只需要把汤汁淋在鱼身即可
Baste the fish with the sauce while braising

0:03:21.040,0:03:22.220
# 无需翻动鲤鱼
You don’t need to flip it over

0:03:26.180,0:03:28.180
# 6分钟之后将鲤鱼捞出摆盘
After 6 minutes, take the carp out of the wok for plating

0:03:43.300,0:03:45.160
# 然后将剩余的汤汁烧开
Then, boil the remaining sauce

0:03:48.360,0:03:51.220
# 汤汁烧开之后加入适量的水淀粉收汁
Once boiled, add in some water starch and reduce the sauce down

0:03:56.840,0:03:59.960
# 最后再加入少许明油拌匀淋在鱼身即可
Lastly, stir in a small amount of Mingyou and pour the sauce over the fish

0:04:14.260,0:04:17.480
# 一道非常美味的年菜红烧鲤鱼就制作完成
A delicious braised carp suitable for the Lunar New Year is now served

0:04:18.660,0:04:19.920
# 下面开始技术总结
Let’s move on to the technical review:

0:04:19.920,0:04:24.100
# 第一，此法适用于大部分鱼类，最好是刺越少越好
Firstly, most types of fish can be used for this dish, but you’d better choose those with fewer fishbones

0:04:24.100,0:04:28.140
# 第二，此法烹饪的口味较为清淡适合老人孩子食用
Secondly, this dish is rather mild and good for elder people and young kids

0:04:28.140,0:04:31.400
# 第三，喜欢重口味的同学请看下期川菜版本
Thirdly, if you like heavier taste, please watch my next video where I will be making a Sichuan version of it

0:04:31.400,0:04:33.080
# 红烧鲤鱼的技术总结完毕（不辣版本 ）
That’s all for the technical review of the braised carp (non-spicy version)
